languages.text: "Пожалуй, вы и правда не похожи на пиратов, что позарились на богатства разрушенной станции. Или подонков, что прислуживают Фелеку. Так кто же вы?"

languages.text: "I'll grant that you do not look like pirates who have come coveting the riches of a wrecked station, or like scoundrels in Felek's service. So who are you?"

languages.text: «Admitiré que no parecen piratas en busca de las riquezas de una estación arruinada ni la clase de canallas que emplea Felek. ¿Quiénes son, pues?».
languages.original_text: "I'll grant that you do not look like pirates who have come coveting the riches of a wrecked station, or like scoundrels in Felek's service. So who are you?"

traits.locale_text: «Admitiré que no parecen piratas en busca de las riquezas de una estación arruinada ni la clase de canallas que emplea Felek. ¿Quiénes son, pues?».

languages.text: 「破滅したステーションの富を目当てにやってきた海賊や、フェレックに仕える悪党ではないことは認めよう。では、あなたは何者なのだ？」
languages.original_text: "I'll grant that you do not look like pirates who have come coveting the riches of a wrecked station, or like scoundrels in Felek's service. So who are you?"

traits.locale_text: 「破滅したステーションの富を目当てにやってきた海賊や、フェレックに仕える悪党ではないことは認めよう。では、あなたは何者なのだ？」

languages.text: "Ich gestehe Euch zu, dass Ihr nicht wie Piraten ausseht, die gekommen sind, um eine zerstörte Station zu plündern. Auch nicht wie Schurken in Feleks Diensten. Wer seid Ihr also?"
languages.original_text: "I'll grant that you do not look like pirates who have come coveting the riches of a wrecked station, or like scoundrels in Felek's service. So who are you?"

languages.text: « Je vous accorde que vous n'avez pas l'allure de pirates venus piller les richesses d'une station en perdition, ni de vauriens au service de Felek. Alors, qui êtes-vous ? »
languages.original_text: "I'll grant that you do not look like pirates who have come coveting the riches of a wrecked station, or like scoundrels in Felek's service. So who are you?"

languages.text: "Harap durumdaki bir istasyonun zenginlikleriyle ağzı sulanan korsanlara veya Felek'in emrindeki şeref yoksunlarına benzemiyorsun, kabul. Kimsin peki sen?"
